Author: Panic-atthepanic
Text: I don't want it to fight back.  I want it to leave me alone.  I'm feeding it and it's still goddamn hungry.  I feel out of control and terrified I'll balloon.

Author: mustyday
Text: I can’t help but I can relate. I can eat over 2000 calories a day and still be physically hungry 30 minutes after dinner. It’s our bodies fighting back and it sucks.
